    55	    `integrate_trial`); it does NOT inspect `trial.commit_sha`. The
    56	    suite therefore covers (b) only transitively, through (a)'s
    57	    enforcement of the lifecycle ordering.
    58	(c) `commit_sha` resolves to a commit on the trial's `branch` in the
    59	    experiment repository — **NOT** wire-observable through chapter 7
    60	    alone (would require the IUT's wire endpoint to validate against
    61	    a real git repo, which the wire spec does not require). This is
